{"1":[[1803,2016,"Commander, this is the latest intel"],[2056,2137,"of missile expert"],[2149,2450,"Mr. Garcia's current location."],[2450,2510,"All set."],[2630,2710,"Let's move."],[4320,4506,"Release him now,"],[4506,4596,"or you'll die!"],[4596,4753,"Who's there? Show yourself!"],[4793,5020,"Intel says Zoe is operating the perimeter!"],[5146,5273,"Better not run into her."],[5313,5484,"Zoe Miller? The one that"],[5499,5703,"soloed an entire terrorist cell?"],[5743,5960,"I heard the President of Valoria"],[6000,6166,"made her Minister of Defense!"],[6250,6296,"Shit!"],[9476,9753,"Mr. Garcia, you're safe with us now."],[9940,10036,"Mission's done."],[10056,10203,"I can finally see my daughter."],[11176,11306,"Mia! Come here!"],[11453,11643,"You must be starving."],[11690,11806,"Here, have some food."]],"2":[[416,606,"Did I say you could eat at the table?"],[720,779,"I'm sorry."],[859,1020,"No, you're meant to crawl on your knees"],[1020,1166,"and lick it up."],[1263,1273,"Go."],[1536,1633,"You stupid little kid."],[1676,1732,"You should have stayed with"],[1746,1923,"your creepy neighbor, Moe."],[1923,2016,"Oh, darling."],[2056,2203,"She wouldn't last a day there."],[2306,2686,"My future King and Queen of Valoria."],[2746,3026,"I am so excited about the Christmas gala"],[3026,3189,"you're throwing tomorrow, David."],[3253,3523,"You're finally gonna be able to show the world"],[3523,3796,"what a great leader of men you are."],[3820,3913,"I wanted to buy that"],[3927,4110,"gold-engraved necklace, David,"],[4110,4456,"but it seems we're a little low on funds."],[4513,4550,"Darling."],[4686,4726,"Relax."],[4746,5063,"Mia's mother is practically our ATM at this point."],[5089,5250,"My mom is not your ATM."],[5276,5516,"Know your place, you dirty little skank."],[5753,5946,"You've stolen almost a million dollars"],[5946,6133,"from my mom in the last ten years."]],"3":[[433,650,"Madam, the president wants to talk."],[830,950,"General Zoe, it's an honor"],[965,1090,"to finally speak with you directly."],[1090,1463,"I hereby officially appoint you as the new"],[1463,1716,"Minister of Defense of Valoria."],[1780,2000,"Yes, but this time I actually..."],[2083,2273,"I just want to report as a mom first."],[2396,2553,"Christmas is coming and I..."],[2626,2786,"I honestly can't wait to see her."],[2819,2880,"Let's go home."],[3136,3379,"Madam, you had to hide your identity"],[3379,3476,"and leave Mia for a decade."],[3576,3720,"The allowances to your brother's family"],[3734,3793,"ensured her comfort,"],[3793,3913,"but now that the nation's secure,"],[3973,4160,"you must be thrilled to reunite with her."],[4233,4333,"Mr. President is asking"],[4347,4453,"if there's anything you wish for"],[4453,4539,"that he might help with."],[4623,4830,"I'm gonna make her the happiest,"],[4872,5139,"wealthiest girl there is."],[5139,5220,"You know there is something"],[5235,5450,"you can do for me."],[5450,5573,"Take me to David's, please."],[5639,5706,"You heard her."],[6079,6183,"Why do you think you're here?"],[6213,6289,"Because your family?"],[6360,6453,"You're a little cash cow."],[6513,6740,"Your mother gets to skim the military budget."],[6783,6943,"As a low-ranking accountant."],[7003,7040,"And we..."],[7196,7276,"we get a free cut."],[7403,7623,"Now, if you don't want your mom to rot in jail,"],[7623,7746,"I suggest you shut up."],[7793,7873,"Call your mother."],[8000,8090,"Do what we say."],[8320,8356,"Hello?"],[8536,8593,"Who is it?"],[8629,8726,"David, it's me."],[8809,8840,"Mom?"]],"4":[[396,616,"Aunt Zoe, welcome! What a lovely surprise."],[656,733,"It's been so long."],[823,969,"Did I just hear Mia's voice?"],[1019,1073,"Uh..."],[1490,1723,"What happened here?"],[1783,1952,"I didn't want to say anything,"],[1964,2223,"but Mia just threw a tantrum"],[2223,2473,"because she's disgusted by my kidney disease"],[2473,2676,"and didn't want to sit with us."],[2803,2993,"That's not the Mia that I remember, but..."],[3063,3229,"Sophia, she has no reason to lie."],[3256,3396,"How could she treat you this way?"],[3439,3486,"Mia?"],[3586,3629,"Coming!"],[4618,4721,"Mia!"],[4853,4956,"Is this how you treat family?"],[5133,5326,"Darling, you need to apologize to her."],[5393,5453,"Now."],[5460,5553,"No, Mom, I..."],[5553,5629,"Mark my word."],[5713,6026,"If you both want to live, keep quiet."],[6196,6404,"No need to apologize, I'm fine."],[6423,6586,"She's just a child."],[6586,6783,"Sophia, just stop, okay?"],[6903,6986,"Don't indulge her."],[6986,7163,"She needs to be held accountable."],[7203,7416,"Well, let's not... let's not overreact."],[7520,7615,"By the way,"],[7629,7933,"about tomorrow's Christmas gala,"],[7933,8103,"we're still $100,000 short."],[8133,8280,"Is there any chance"],[8280,8546,"you could front us the difference?"],[8546,8689,"I will pay you back, of course."],[8712,8816,"You have my word, Aunt Zoe."],[8816,8977,"Just that at the Christmas gala"],[8977,9210,"there will be a bunch of VIPs"],[9210,9563,"and we need the event to strengthen our"],[9600,9866,"relationships with CEOs and business elites."],[9913,9976,"It's fine."],[10009,10303,"Look, you've been watching her for 10 years now."],[10443,10563,"It's the least I could do."],[10723,10856,"Mom, don't give them any money!"]],"5":[[163,206,"Mia..."],[320,370,"What's wrong?"],[593,729,"She looks devastated."],[856,986,"Is there something going on here?"],[1023,1216,"Mia, is there something that you're hiding from me?"],[1380,1633,"No. No. No, I was just..."],[1873,2116,"I think 100,000 is too much money."],[2173,2213,"Darling."],[2330,2516,"Look, you're my only child."],[2546,2723,"And besides what you just did to Sophia,"],[2753,2933,"I mean, she deserves some compensation."],[3320,3386,"Here's..."],[3516,3753,"200,000. Just take it."],[3806,4060,"Oh, wonderful. Thank you, Zoe."],[4136,4296,"Thank you so much, Aunt Zoe."],[4383,4563,"You must be exhausted from your travels."],[4563,4723,"I'll have the driver take you to your hotel."],[4843,4900,"Mom?"],[5096,5239,"Can you take me with you?"],[5433,5616,"Darling, I just got into the country."],[5636,5773,"I need a few days."],[5773,5906,"I'm gonna sort some stuff out."],[5956,6116,"And I'll come and get you."],[6556,6676,"Are you not happy here?"],[6700,6740,"Or..."],[6786,6929,"Of course she's happy."],[6950,7116,"Don't let us keep you."],[7346,7406,"Okay."],[7440,7503,"Hey, come on."],[8033,8159,"I miss you. I love you."],[8259,8350,"I'll see you soon, okay?"],[8350,8386,"Let's go."],[8753,8806,"Thank you."],[8806,8996,"Thank you so much for taking good care of her."],[9013,9063,"Of course."],[9093,9116,"Yes."],[9173,9209,"Okay."],[9526,9583,"Mom!"]],"6":[[86,240,"If your mother gets suspicious"],[256,400,"and we don't cash that money,"],[400,600,"I'm gonna send her to the colonial island"],[626,919,"and our customers will take very good care of her."],[946,1133,"I hear they skin people alive over there."],[1153,1333,"Is that really what you want, sweetie?"],[1366,1503,"Please, please don't hurt my mom."],[1996,2030,"Yes?"],[2153,2350,"Yeah, great, absolutely."],[2710,2783,"Great news."],[2853,3023,"The Minister of Defence is coming to"],[3023,3110,"to our Christmas Gala tomorrow."],[3273,3414,"What? Since when"],[3419,3716,"does the Harris Group have such clout?"],[3723,3910,"Well, obviously it's me."],[3976,4246,"My uncle just reunited with his long lost son,"],[4246,4470,"Jacob Marley, the new senator,"],[4539,4716,"and the Minister of Defence's"],[4734,4810,"favourite protege."],[4810,5050,"If we can secure the Minister,"],[5060,5283,"the Harris Group would skyrocket."],[5283,5416,"Once Robert gets here tomorrow,"],[5429,5650,"we'll just gift-wrap this little present for him"],[5650,5800,"so she can make herself useful."],[5893,6083,"No man of his stature has probably never tasted..."],[6176,6289,"gutter filth like her."],[6383,6490,"He might enjoy the novelty."],[6663,6853,"Please, please, I did everything you asked."],[6853,6916,"Shut up!"],[6993,7263,"While I might still just sell you to the highest bidder."],[7263,7433,"Quit whining."],[7566,7640,"I'll kill you!"],[8063,8116,"Get off!"],[8440,8559,"Save your energy."],[8586,8816,"You'll need it tomorrow to serve Mr. Robert,"],[8816,8986,"and if you disappoint him,"],[9016,9236,"we will punish your mother accordingly."]],"7":[[173,260,"Uncle Robert."],[279,696,"This is my cousin Mia, pure and untouched."],[766,850,"All for you to enjoy."],[1003,1409,"Very good. You know, I do enjoy mentoring the youth."],[1500,1563,"Where is she?"],[1626,1736,"She's in the upstairs bedroom,"],[1834,1956,"just waiting for you."],[1956,2023,"Very good."],[2163,2450,"You have earned the future favor of the Harris Group."],[3346,3573,"Could you do me a favor? Go get the gifts."],[3616,3800,"It's Mia's first Christmas with me and I"],[3833,3966,"want to give her a big surprise."],[3986,4056,"Understood, Madam."],[4103,4242,"Mr. President has everything prepared"],[4242,4303,"for you."],[4303,4379,"Great. Thank you."],[4963,5006,"David!"],[5096,5160,"Aunt Zoe!"],[5160,5210,"Hi!"],[5210,5266,"Hi, welcome!"],[5266,5329,"How are you?"],[5329,5413,"Merry Christmas, welcome!"],[5413,5460,"Hi!"],[5493,5629,"You're early."],[5629,5676,"Where's Mia?"],[5766,5926,"I'm really excited to see her."],[5976,6066,"Why are you alone?"],[6116,6265,"Oh, she overslept."],[6265,6389,"She's still getting ready upstairs."],[6389,6429,"Oh."],[6590,6690,"You must be spoiling her."],[6733,6940,"You know, only the best for family."],[6940,7023,"Just let her be."],[7033,7146,"You should be enjoying the party."],[7166,7323,"Let me take you upstairs to the VIP lounge."],[7383,7413,"Okay."],[7413,7523,"Come on. Come on."],[7523,7626,"Fine. Yeah."],[8173,8300,"Wakey wakey."]],"8":[[50,199,"Good morning, sunshine."],[393,638,"Such a beautiful little present"],[638,834,"and all wrapped up tight."],[1880,1940,"Hey!"],[1940,2049,"Stay away from me!"],[2060,2402,"No, no, no. You just relax."],[2505,2812,"But, you know, the more you struggle,"],[2826,3111,"the more I'm going to enjoy this."],[3440,3571,"Oh yeah."],[3579,3779,"Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!"],[3779,3850,"Mom!"],[3960,4069,"Mom!"],[4486,4632,"It sounded like Mia."],[4679,4888,"That's just the jet lag messing with your head."]],"9":[[30,229,"Come on, you should enjoy the party. Let's go."],[493,686,"Now you listen to me."],[830,1006,"You be a good girl."],[1069,1290,"Or I'll kill Zoe and make you watch."],[1806,1906,"Okay, I'll be quiet."],[1956,2080,"Oh, come on."],[2189,2456,"Stop crying. You're ruining the mood."],[2643,2683,"Oh, look."],[2810,2946,"Now I'm not in the mood."],[3019,3293,"You're gonna have to convince me all over again."],[3389,3443,"Well?"],[4439,4516,"Any news for me?"],[4620,4646,"Henry."],[4689,4756,"Lock her in."],[4800,4960,"If she escapes, you're dead."],[5076,5110,"Done."]],"10":[[63,153,"Make yourself comfortable."],[590,670,"Here you go."],[1130,1219,"So happy to have you here."],[1303,1499,"I want you to relax, enjoy the party,"],[1516,1623,"and I'll go fetch Mia."],[1623,1716,"Great. Thanks."],[2536,2663,"Where is the Minister of Defense?"],[2663,2753,"It's been three hours."],[2883,3143,"David Harris can't be a liar, can he?"],[3166,3404,"Is the Minister of Defense really"],[3416,3583,"coming to this shabby party?"],[3583,3810,"Darling, we could be at the French Ambassador's gala."],[3810,4063,"This reeks of new money desperation."],[4103,4143,"Darling,"],[4183,4336,"Harris Group's Christmas miracle?"],[4429,4546,"More like a Christmas sham."],[4566,4729,"Call your uncle now."],[5186,5543,"Ladies and gentlemen, let us be patient."],[5600,5900,"The Minister has sacrificed a lot for all of us."],[5953,6081,"The least we could do is"],[6094,6329,"show our respect and remain calm."],[6329,6379,"It's true."],[6416,6583,"He had a tough year fighting battles overseas."],[6676,6956,"I can't wait to meet the Minister in person."],[7379,7463,"Hello, I'm coming in."],[7843,7873,"Fuck!"],[7976,8059,"Get back here!"],[8170,8279,"Please help me."],[8279,8390,"You have to save my mom."]],"11":[[0,80,"Jesus, what happened?"],[110,236,"David's been holding me hostage."],[276,381,"He and Sophia have stolen"],[381,573,"over a million dollars from my mother."],[573,746,"This whole party's to further his agenda."],[796,1059,"And now he's trying to offer me as a gift to Robert."],[1273,1413,"That bitch is going to ruin everything."],[2706,2936,"My ungrateful sister, you little liar."],[3003,3136,"We sheltered you, we fed you."],[3150,3239,"Is this how you repay us?"],[3293,3466,"Ungrateful wretch."],[3626,3834,"How dare you slander my uncle"],[3841,4073,"at our holiday party."],[4073,4463,"I am the father of Senator Jacob Marley."],[4496,4833,"Why would I touch gutter trash like you?"],[4966,5139,"You are just a spiteful liar."],[5183,5313,"No, I'm not lying."],[5313,5463,"Please, you have to believe me."],[5496,5560,"Take her away."],[5603,5629,"Now."],[5726,5760,"Wait!"],[5786,5994,"At this very important Christmas Gala,"],[6048,6286,"we must use this little bitch!"],[6286,6566,"Mia's lies about Robert are ruining our reputation!"],[6636,6890,"We shall behold the dignity"],[6931,7184,"and honor of the Harris family!"]],"12":[[16,143,"What a sly little bitch."],[220,358,"She must be a bastard brat"],[392,540,"from the wrong side of the bed."],[540,659,"Pathetic, accusing Robert."],[659,873,"He's a distinguished man of valor in Valoria."],[909,1100,"You're a disgrace to all women."],[1263,1326,"They're lying!"],[1386,1453,"Shut up!"],[1483,1703,"Or I'll go drag your little soldier mom down here."],[1723,1789,"And I will break her."],[1796,1973,"Please don't, she didn't do anything."],[2186,2286,"It's too late for mercy."],[2426,2633,"Lick my shoes clean."],[2723,2986,"And maybe I'll spare your pathetic mother."],[3723,3773,"Too slow!"],[5803,5923,"Now crawl through the glass."],[6046,6379,"Crawl!"],[6379,6450,"Faster!"],[6450,8793,"Crawl faster!"],[8900,9023,"I'll always love you."],[9913,9959,"Hey."],[10023,10216,"I did it. Please save my mom."],[10309,10476,"Begging's beneath you now."],[10973,11026,"Stop!"],[11070,11240,"Who dares touch my daughter?"]],"13":[[66,139,"I don't get it."],[139,350,"Why is David gifting Mia to Robert?"],[486,596,"I'd have taken her first."],[616,693,"Taboo tastes, eh boss?"],[916,1030,"You're not wrong there."],[5503,5660,"Aunt Zoey!"],[5660,5743,"Where are you going?"],[5743,5820,"Henry, get out of the way."],[5846,5916,"I'm looking for Mia."],[5953,5993,"Mia?"],[6073,6310,"Oh no, she's not free right now to see you."],[6379,6505,"She's too busy getting"],[6505,6790,"acquainted with Uncle Robert."],[6790,6856,"What do you mean?"],[6973,7079,"I guess I can tell you."],[7103,7296,"You are just a retired soldier."],[7356,7720,"Mia's lived worse than a beggar for all of these years."],[7829,7943,"But that's impossible."],[8053,8216,"I just, I saw her yesterday."],[8309,8453,"Did they tell you that she was fine?"],[8573,8806,"Did David beg you for money?"],[9083,9240,"You are so gullible."],[9303,9543,"No wonder he swindled millions from you."],[9670,9743,"You monster."],[9846,9976,"Don't you have any laws?"]],"14":[[23,63,"The law?"],[189,323,"Bullshit!"],[456,673,"David used Mia as a little cash cow."],[673,866,"She's lived like trash for all of these years."],[893,1083,"And there's nothing you can do."],[1100,1433,"Jacob, Grace's cousin is Valoria's senator."],[1440,1623,"Crushing you two will be like crushing ants."],[2316,2496,"See how your precious daughter grovels?"],[2786,2916,"I think she looks rather cute."],[3003,3180,"Just pinch her little cheeks, huh?"],[3473,3703,"Tears rolling down her face"],[3734,4276,"just makes those cheeks irresistible."],[4276,4356,"Ten years."],[4476,4563,"Ten years of torture."],[4703,4843,"Ten years of lies?"],[4929,5346,"Your funeral is tonight, you piece of shit!"]],"15":[[30,310,"I did what you asked! Please let my mom go!"],[363,796,"Aww, darling. I said I'd consider it."],[863,1233,"And after careful consideration..."],[1413,1476,"Denied!"],[1719,1873,"You liar! I'll kill you!"],[2586,2886,"You ruined my dress, bitch."],[2913,3033,"Can someone strip her?"],[3063,3276,"Let her know how it feels to be humiliated."],[3329,3439,"Let me handle that."],[3486,3583,"What? No!"],[3750,3960,"What kind of animals make the laws here?"],[4010,4246,"I make the laws here. Strip her and throw her out!"],[4410,4463,"Stop!"],[4556,4733,"Who dares touch my daughter?"]],"16":[[3,236,"Let me see who is touching Mia!"],[676,806,"Mom, I'm so sorry."],[863,1096,"David was stealing from you for years and I knew."],[1096,1333,"I'm sorry, it's my fault. I didn't mean it."],[1336,1543,"Sweetheart, it's ok."],[1913,2016,"Are you hurt anywhere else?"],[2076,2096,"No."],[2183,2316,"That's fine, as long as you're safe."],[2543,2726,"I should be begging your forgiveness."],[3039,3236,"Ten years and you were tortured."],[3300,3470,"I called you ungrateful."],[3579,3650,"Please..."],[3956,4033,"Forgive me."],[4403,4496,"You, bitch!"],[4563,4666,"You hurt my boy Henry?"],[4866,5036,"Neither of you gets out of here alive!"],[5110,5300,"No, no, please don't take her!"],[5300,5446,"Punish me! Take me instead!"],[5496,5523,"No."],[5623,5800,"No one hurts you, not now."],[5856,5920,"Not ever."],[5989,6203,"And every tear that you shed,"],[6266,6543,"they will repay with blood."]],"17":[[0,173,"Do you really think you can defend"],[173,363,"this trashy daughter of yours?"],[443,586,"Look at yourself!"],[586,843,"How dare you ruin my son's banquet!"],[890,1156,"I will end both of you! You first!"],[1156,1413,"No, no, wait! Please don't take my mom!"],[1613,1880,"You better not touch me."],[2103,2343,"How dare you resist me? Let go!"],[2469,2556,"This is for Mia."],[2800,2966,"This is for your arrogance."],[3200,3403,"This is for torturing Mia!"],[4163,4500,"You bitch! You dare strike me?!"],[5226,5270,"Mama!"],[5546,5663,"How dare you touch my mother?"],[5706,5883,"I swear, kneel and beg for mercy,"],[5883,6053,"or I swear I will slaughter you and your daughter!"],[6083,6210,"You want me to beg for mercy?"],[6256,6293,"Yeah."],[6293,6333,"Really?"],[6443,6646,"Today's funeral will be yours!"]],"18":[[86,160,"Stay back."],[500,670,"Guards? Get in here now!"],[683,756,"Kill her!"],[756,823,"Kill her now!"],[869,923,"Kill her!"],[1433,1480,"Get her!"],[3673,3726,"Oh my..."],[4576,4689,"Hey, come on!"],[4826,5028,"Impossible! I paid thousands"],[5028,5629,"for this top mercenary!"],[5629,5781,"You know, I did come here"],[5831,6089,"to give the Harris family a fortune."],[6089,6150,"But now?"],[6226,6375,"You guys aren't even worth"],[6375,6576,"the bullet it would take to end you."],[6576,6666,"Rabid dogs..."],[6779,6943,"They don't deserve crowns."],[7046,7146,"Where are you going?"],[7370,7446,"I wasn't done yet."],[7483,7740,"Retired army hag with no husband to protect her?"],[7803,7986,"What fortune could she possibly offer?"],[8046,8303,"She barely scraped together one million in ten years."],[8303,8426,"She's just bluffing me."],[8490,8553,"Come on!"],[8600,8690,"Seize this bitch!"],[8946,9036,"Guards, get her!"]],"19":[[343,426,"Are you ok?"],[966,1196,"I'll take any punishment, please don't hurt her!"],[1556,1596,"Shut up!"],[1689,1813,"Your mother hit Henry."],[1876,2050,"She'll pay, or you both die here."],[2139,2650,"David, you tortured Mia, your own cousin, for years!"],[2726,3016,"You deserve to rot in hell."],[3186,3296,"That's such a weak threat."],[3379,3489,"Let me enlighten you."],[3520,3649,"I kept your daughter chained up"],[3651,3896,"like a dog for ten years."],[3896,4029,"I whipped her when I was bored."],[4056,4146,"I fed her scraps."],[4329,4650,"And I stole every penny you sent."],[4746,4779,"And you?"],[4836,4970,"You couldn't even stop me."],[4989,5136,"Now that is real power."],[5446,5723,"You think you can play God because you have power?"]],"20":[[36,263,"Power is the ultimate law."],[376,546,"It's more valuable than your lives."],[653,836,"Well, by that logic,"],[866,1186,"then you should all die in this poisonous house."],[1253,1413,"Hmm. Big words."],[1486,1763,"Where is that huge tribute you keep talking about?"],[1796,1833,"Show us."],[1876,1933,"Bring it out."],[2006,2223,"If you do, I'll gift wrap my own corpse."],[2330,2576,"Is death what you really want?"],[3063,3261,"James, deploy the troops"],[3285,3623,"in ten minutes at David's house."],[3623,3723,"His front doorstep."],[3779,3829,"Ten minutes?"],[3873,4023,"You couldn't get that tribute in ten years."],[4323,4563,"Pathetic pensioner playing billionaire."],[5706,5800,"The tribute arrives."]],"21":[[3,123,"The tribute arrives."],[236,450,"Gift one, a tray of gold bars."],[540,846,"Gift two, a limited edition Rolls-Royce Phantom."],[1000,1223,"Gift 3, a mansion in downtown."],[1630,2066,"That's 20 million dollars worth of gifts! From her?"],[2133,2303,"Our entire networth is 30 million."],[2332,2500,"This could triple our power."],[2500,2610,"Mom, are these yours?"],[2630,2856,"I told James to send a proper tribute."],[2883,2943,"This?"],[3063,3296,"This is bargain-bin trash."],[3453,3676,"20 million trash? Who the hell is she?"],[3686,4020,"Did you fools really think she could afford this?"],[4060,4189,"Wait, Grace."],[4243,4363,"You arranged this?"],[4429,4476,"Obviously."],[4573,4870,"Um, may I ask who these gifts are from?"]],"22":[[3,356,"These gifts are from Senator Jacob Marley for Miss Grace."],[503,773,"My cousin Jacob just reclaimed his senate seat."],[823,1086,"So naturally, these honors are for me."],[1133,1259,"You shameless leech."],[1369,1506,"You dare claim the senator's gifts?"],[1536,1750,"A wash-up soldier playing tycoon?"],[1776,1856,"Embarrassing."],[2083,2306,"I'm sorry, did I actually claim that?"],[2366,2700,"No, because my daughter deserves a proper tribute."],[2746,2976,"You couldn't afford these gifts in 10 lifetimes."],[2980,3069,"Enough with the games!"],[3160,3346,"Kneel and beg for your life! Or I swear I will..."],[3346,3683,"Ah, ah, ah, ah! I'm sorry. Careful, David."],[3713,3879,"You're rushing your own funeral."]],"23":[[3,223,"How dare you threaten David after"],[223,389,"trying to steal the Senator's gifts?"],[443,523,"Know your place."],[613,700,"Steal?"],[946,1161,"You guys think that these trinkets"],[1189,1360,"are something special."],[1360,1463,"But let me tell you something."],[1506,1876,"I wouldn't wipe my shoes with them."],[2183,2383,"How dare you ruin the Senator's gifts?"],[2433,2683,"You lunatic! Do you know how much these are worth?"],[2716,2846,"You're gonna pay for this!"],[2850,3036,"These gifts aren't even worth a penny."],[3693,4033,"You better bring back better gifts by sunset,"],[4079,4500,"or you and your daughter will die like stray dogs!"],[4613,4929,"Take Mia and run, you've angered the Senator's kin."],[5113,5306,"After humiliating the Harris family,"],[5306,5436,"you will die on your knees."]],"24":[[3,343,"My newfound son is Senator Jacob Marley."],[343,520,"His power spans continents."],[566,696,"You dare destroy my gifts?"],[733,846,"If David spares you,"],[986,1046,"I won't."],[1146,1380,"Senator, please, we'll handle this."],[1613,1803,"Bring your tribute now."],[1846,2069,"Or I swear I'll bury you both alive in my backyard."],[2069,2203,"Open your eyes, boy."],[2250,2639,"Because this, this is what a real tribute looks like."],[2686,2869,"5,000 acres of oil fields,"],[2869,3126,"gifted by the crown prince of the kingdom of Asura."],[3186,3277,"A private bank,"],[3319,3593,"presented by the countess of Lule Island."],[3593,3713,"A set of heirloom jewels,"],[3750,3953,"bestowed by the Queen of Amantay."],[4060,4310,"Finally, from the Duchess of Barada,"],[4343,4483,"who has been granted authority"],[4533,4673,"by Her Majesty the Queen"],[4686,4979,"to bestow a noble title upon Miss Mia."],[5596,5800,"These oil fields alone are worth billions."],[5823,6010,"How did a disgruntled veteran pull this off?"],[6056,6260,"Do you still think that your trash compares?"],[6296,6520,"Does anybody want to challenge my gifts?"],[6553,6609,"Anyone else?"],[6656,6826,"Mom, are these gifts really for me?"],[6893,7243,"Sweetheart, I owe you way more than that."],[7450,7759,"You guys said that power buys people,"],[7759,7838,"well then I must be the"],[7854,8156,"most powerful person in the room."],[8156,8470,"So whose head is gonna be collected first?"]],"25":[[16,150,"A retired grunt with millions?"],[260,293,"How?"],[323,483,"Probably embezzled military money"],[503,683,"to play rich mommy with."],[683,827,"My Senator cousin's net"],[839,1050,"worth barely touches 10 billion."],[1050,1173,"You're just a broke veteran."],[1256,1306,"What did you..."],[1376,1488,"Borrow these gifts"],[1488,1766,"like my sister steals my jewelry for dates?"],[1766,1813,"Pathetic."],[1880,1936,"Pathetic bluff."],[2000,2113,"You'll die for this charade."],[2206,2330,"My mom never lied."],[2330,2500,"Well maybe she whored herself out to the generals."],[2660,2813,"But even that wouldn't earn this."],[2886,2950,"Borrowed?"],[3123,3356,"You guys, don't be ridiculous."],[3403,3547,"You guys just don't even know"],[3547,3723,"what power really is."],[3800,3823,"Enough."],[3976,4270,"Execute them before the Minister of Defense arrives."],[4329,4465,"What if I actually told you that..."],[4581,4847,"I am the Minister of Defense?"]],"26":[[3,139,"You delusional bitch."],[246,603,"You're just pretending to be the Minister of Defense."],[716,790,"Seize her."],[1663,1843,"David, get more men."],[1886,1943,"Now!"],[2000,2153,"Stop! Please don't hurt my mom."],[2213,2460,"Mia, honey, they can't harm me. Okay?"],[2500,2613,"Okay, I trust you."],[2716,3025,"Tonight, I am gonna pay back"],[3042,3315,"every debt that you did to her."],[3316,3543,"You batshit crazy woman. What are you..."],[3543,3643,"Hit the protocal, now."],[3710,3729,"What?"],[3920,4033,"It's the Minister's elite guards."],[4086,4233,"This is ridiculous!"],[4363,4423,"Oh, wait!"],[4423,4496,"Leave us alone!"],[4533,4553,"What?"],[4596,5006,"If privilege can really purchase life, well..."],[5060,5199,"I say we just go ahead and"],[5211,5323,"proceed with this transaction."],[5323,5400,"Wouldn't that be fun?"]],"27":[[16,160,"Release me! Or I'll..."],[550,593,"No!"],[676,740,"My son!"],[790,963,"You lunatic! I'll kill you!"],[1200,1259,"David!"],[1296,1366,"Henry!"],[1440,1748,"You all will suffer every pain and agony"],[1761,1900,"that you put Mia in."],[1900,2016,"It's your turn."],[2103,2210,"These are your family!"],[2210,2369,"I mean, their crimes don't warrant death!"],[2423,2589,"They stopped being my family"],[2589,2776,"the second that they messed with Mia."],[2796,2893,"Execute them all!"],[2969,3019,"Stop!"]],"28":[[16,223,"Mom, please don't kill anyone else, I'm scared!"],[276,420,"Sweetheart, don't be scared."],[439,726,"This is what you call justice, ok?"],[726,926,"No. Isn't it enough that you're back?"],[973,1116,"Please, I don't want you to go to prison!"],[1163,1269,"I'm not gonna go to prison,"],[1373,1569,"for these monsters."],[1660,1755,"You're insane!"],[1776,1943,"You really think you're gonna get away?"],[1943,2126,"Mom, please don't hurt anyone, I'm scared!"],[2183,2563,"You dare spill blood at a Christmas gala?"],[2636,2796,"Look, the Prime Minister is coming,"],[2796,2913,"and when he arrives,"],[2980,3096,"you will pay."],[3166,3466,"What if I really am then Minister of Defence?"],[3606,3653,"What?"]],"29":[[0,156,"You're really the Minister of Defense?"],[223,456,"The national hero who protects our country?"],[576,698,"Sweetheart, I might have been able"],[698,786,"to defend this country,"],[786,1019,"but I did a terrible job at raising you."],[1153,1226,"But I..."],[1309,1424,"But I'm gonna make them pay"],[1424,1656,"for what they did to you, okay?"],[1656,1810,"That's impossible."],[1893,2153,"The Prime Minister is not a woman."],[2216,2416,"Your little charade ends now."],[2473,2673,"My cousin, the Senator, is on his way."],[2716,2866,"In 30 minutes, you're finished!"],[2926,3114,"You know, I think that 30 minutes is..."],[3166,3243,"it's way too generous."],[3243,3400,"Actually, what I think you should do is"],[3401,3565,"you should just go ahead and call Jacob"],[3589,3800,"and tell him to crawl here in 10 minutes."],[3826,3967,"And if he's not here in 10 minutes,"],[3987,4143,"he can lose his Senate seat."]],"30":[[3,233,"You can't possibly be the Minister of Defense."],[266,493,"You're just a washed up soldier, it's laughable."],[533,590,"That's right."],[600,716,"The Minister's a war legend."],[716,813,"Not some deranged hag."],[836,1130,"She's obviously just posing as the Minister."],[1180,1466,"We cannot let this weird woman"],[1466,1813,"impersonate your Senator's son adoptive mother."],[1863,2193,"When my son arrives, this impersonator"],[2226,2466,"will be crushed by my son, the Senator."],[2686,2760,"Thank you, Robert."],[2860,3150,"Please make sure he punishes her mercilessly."],[3183,3336,"A life for a life!"],[3470,3646,"You can trust my son's integrity."],[3776,4050,"He'll make sure that he crushes that impersonator."],[4173,4483,"When Jacob arrives, your little act ends."],[4520,4593,"Permanently."],[4593,4810,"I actually created Valoria's security."],[4810,4953,"And I gave Jacob his job."],[4983,5229,"Nobody questions me, especially him."],[5283,5433,"Liar, you're... you're nothing!"],[5503,5603,"I can vouch for her."]],"31":[[90,293,"Who dares impersonate the Minister of Defense"],[336,493,"and destroy the gifts I sent?"],[583,703,"They're begging for death."],[1453,1543,"Mr. James."],[1590,1889,"Jacob, get to the Christmas Gala in 10 minutes,"],[1946,2096,"or I'll strip you of your senator title."],[2169,2210,"Now!"],[2373,2430,"Let's go."],[2489,2643,"We have to be at David's house in 10 minutes."],[2673,2726,"Hurry up!"],[2793,2943,"Keep putting on this charade."],[3013,3460,"When my son, the senator, arrives, you'll all regret this."],[3573,3766,"The Minister's got an armed convoy."],[3843,3900,"Where's yours?"],[4023,4096,"Imposter."],[4146,4243,"Damn right."],[4293,4556,"My son is a senator so he knows"],[4556,4726,"what the Prime Minister looks like."],[4743,4899,"Tell Jacob to bring his troops."],[4929,5026,"End her now!"],[5026,5273,"Okay, that's my phone. Don't shoot."],[5383,5520,"It's probably Jacob."],[5579,5782,"I'm just going to reach slowly"],[5803,6196,"and I'll answer. Okay?"],[6196,6479,"Wait, that woman's lackey just called Jacob"],[6479,6609,"and now he's calling back?"],[6656,6826,"Could she be the minister?"]],"32":[[13,253,"Relax. I'm gonna answer this call."],[316,566,"Jacob, you're on speaker. What's happening?"],[696,986,"That woman's a fraud. She even got me scolded."],[1026,1113,"I'll be there in minutes."],[1113,1416,"Just wait till I tear apart this imposter pretending."],[1843,1963,"Look, you heard him."],[2016,2373,"This imposter impersonated the Minister of Defence"],[2373,2556,"and dragged my son the Senator"],[2605,2739,"into this whole mess."],[2739,2880,"When the Senator gets here,"],[2912,3093,"you will pay for this."],[3093,3233,"Your blood for his blood."],[3293,3443,"No, my mom would never lie."],[3500,3633,"She really is the Minister."],[3766,4033,"Are you ok? Mia?"],[4033,4163,"No, she'd never."],[4263,4316,"Mia!"],[4516,4576,"Come on."],[4593,4660,"She's critical."],[4689,4813,"We need to get her to a hospital now."],[4873,5086,"No one is leaving here."],[5176,5286,"Until Jacob arrives."],[5353,5446,"Don't try to escape."]],"33":[[16,106,"Mia's critical."],[156,253,"She might have minutes to live."],[261,416,"We have to get her to a hospital."],[416,533,"Guards, surround them!"],[723,919,"No one is leaving."],[953,1136,"This whole mother-daughter act"],[1136,1559,"is a charade to distract Jacob from exposing them."],[1619,1913,"That old hag isn't going anywhere in Valoria."],[1946,2100,"Try to stop me."],[3253,3593,"Jacob is almost here. You won't escape."],[3723,3766,"Move!"],[3766,3829,"Get out of my way!"],[3829,3873,"Move!"],[3926,4100,"Senator Jacob has arrived."]],"34":[[3,113,"The senator is here."],[150,286,"Maybe the minister is with him."],[316,500,"Quick, let's go greet them. Come."],[776,1043,"Jacob has arrived. Finally."],[3076,3183,"Severe malnutrition."],[3229,3343,"Systemic injuries."],[3450,3570,"I don't know how she survived."],[3720,3820,"Monsters."],[4006,4106,"What did they do to you?"],[4210,4356,"I should have come earlier."],[4503,4596,"I'm so sorry."],[4886,4966,"It's okay, Mom."],[5050,5203,"It doesn't hurt that much."],[5323,5420,"I'll be better soon."],[5993,6093,"I will make them pay."],[6243,6360,"Every last one of them."],[6406,6446,"Mom."],[6523,6596,"It's over."]],"35":[[250,393,"Mom, this is my friend Lina."],[629,676,"It's okay."],[1660,1756,"I wash them clean."],[1813,1976,"They are safe, I promise."],[2246,2610,"Lina's parents died as war heroes for Valoria."],[2646,2769,"She's adopted."],[2863,2980,"That's all she could afford."],[3093,3279,"Valoria provides compensation"],[3280,3433,"to fallen heroes."],[3433,3686,"She should be compensated. She shouldn't be struggling."],[3886,3950,"It's complicated."],[4023,4126,"Well explain."],[4153,4406,"I never saw a single coin of that compensation."],[4529,4790,"Senator Jacob's newly found father"],[4814,5031,"took it all for his villas."]],"36":[[3,103,"Those bastards."],[180,406,"Stealing compensation from Valoria's war heroes?"],[486,729,"This is beyond lawless. They spit on our laws."],[836,890,"James?"],[980,1026,"Ma'am."],[1093,1186,"This ends now."],[1226,1459,"You are walking towards your death."],[1459,1523,"What do you mean?"],[1546,1753,"Senator Jacob isn't just the Secretary's protege."],[1773,2013,"He is President Louis Scott's golden boy."],[2033,2173,"He controls everything."],[2200,2500,"Compensation, funds, healthcare, real estate."],[2530,2766,"And his father is the one who is drying people out."],[2773,2876,"You cannot win."],[3046,3093,"What?"],[3506,3596,"Mia's medical bill."],[3676,3796,"$500,000?"],[3966,4053,"Those parasites!"],[4123,4333,"Now they're extorting money from hospitals?"],[4426,4586,"We need to burn them down."],[4839,4886,"Oh no..."],[5733,5766,"Mom?"]],"37":[[386,620,"Please, please, please!"],[690,766,"Get out of my way!"],[1046,1130,"You can't take this."],[1283,1403,"You can't take this money."],[1446,1653,"This money is my parent's death benefits."],[1713,1853,"Their sacrifice for Valoria."],[1876,2038,"Without it I cannot pay tuition."],[2063,2266,"I'll have to drop out."],[2266,2426,"You know, maybe I'll pay for your education."],[2543,2746,"You see this crazy bitch ruined me and hurt my arm,"],[2746,3080,"so I've got a lot of frustration to take out."],[3376,3589,"So maybe if you can help me blow off some steam,"],[3763,3846,"I can pay for your fees."],[4003,4126,"Sounds like a deal, right?"],[5139,5236,"Let me go."],[5236,5360,"How about you beg for me, huh?"]],"38":[[193,363,"David, you will die!"],[676,916,"Her parents fought and died for Valoria."],[943,1116,"And yet you took her money?"],[1156,1276,"You are a piece of shit!"],[1316,1383,"So what?"],[1426,1616,"You pissed off every important figure in Valoria."],[1663,1819,"Beg on your knees, or you'll die screaming."],[1869,1906,"Shut it."],[1933,2183,"If it wasn't for her parents, you wouldn't even be here."],[2260,2389,"I don't see how that's my concern."],[2419,2606,"Dying is lower class fate, it's not mine."],[2656,2783,"Apologize to Lena now."],[2850,2946,"Or you will die."],[3000,3106,"Beg a gutter rat's pardon?"],[3183,3233,"Never."],[4520,4669,"Fuck you! What the hell are you doing,"],[4683,4800,"you crazy bitch?"],[4800,5156,"Apologize to everybody that you ever disrespected now."],[5183,5286,"Touch me once again,"],[5326,5496,"and I swear I'll make her pay once you're gone."],[5503,5773,"They'll kill you for this. I'm not worth your life."]],"39":[[26,400,"Sweetheart, your parents deserve respect"],[451,544,"and so do you."],[623,676,"Pathetic."],[850,966,"Playing saviour to some trash."],[1043,1190,"I swear if you cross me one more time,"],[1190,1350,"I will bury your entire family."],[1383,1576,"Rot in hell, you vile scum!"],[2243,2369,"Fuck you, I'll kill you."],[2410,2456,"Try."],[2553,2733,"Guards, get in here. Now!"],[2743,2930,"Run, please. They will kill you."],[3016,3239,"Don't worry. My mom is unstoppable."],[3389,3486,"Bullies with weapons."],[3603,3679,"This will be fun."],[3720,3779,"Kill them!"]],"40":[[43,229,"See? I told you my mom's unstoppable."],[326,376,"Incredible."],[693,809,"She's killing people again."],[833,959,"The crazy bitch, she's a monster."],[1023,1163,"No one can save you now."],[1236,1280,"Maggot."],[1333,1390,"No, no, stay back."],[1436,1519,"You can't kill me."],[1559,1743,"Senator Jacobs will destroy you if you touch me."],[1793,1930,"What are you gonna do now, huh?"],[2100,2230,"Stand down."],[2553,2700,"With this token, I'm now the second most"],[2700,2939,"powerful man in town next to Senator Jacob."],[3069,3216,"Do you dare challenge me?"],[3260,3453,"You're dead, you hear me?"],[3453,3516,"You're dead."],[3800,3863,"Try me."],[4086,4133,"Hey!"],[4220,4310,"You listen?"],[4363,4546,"You think the rules don't apply to you?"],[4870,4963,"What are you gonna do?"],[5066,5120,"Shoot her."]],"41":[[326,596,"Today, we settle debts old and new."],[663,756,"With the same bullet."],[996,1106,"One wrong move from your men."],[1386,1503,"And your brains hit the floor."],[1766,2103,"I'm Senator Jacob's biological father."],[2206,2393,"You can't touch me."],[2686,2726,"Yeah."],[2810,2916,"Well, I adopted him."],[3039,3223,"So if anybody gets to kill him, it's me."],[3333,3600,"So what? You just slither into his life?"],[3713,3773,"What's your plan?"],[3863,4006,"I'm not here to answer questions"],[4021,4253,"from a retired grunt."],[4253,4356,"I'm his real father"],[4383,4616,"and that outweighs your claim of motherhood."],[4700,4733,"Fine."],[4803,4936,"James, just kill him."],[4983,5020,"Yes ma'am."],[5443,5526,"Wait, uncle James!"],[5643,5876,"Mom, killing Robert won't fix anything."],[5876,6003,"It's not going to stop the suffering."],[6003,6233,"But she's dying! We need to save her now!"],[6523,6596,"Uncle Robert!"]],"42":[[43,210,"She's crashing! We need surgery!"],[223,279,"Now!"],[376,496,"What do you think you're doing?"],[523,666,"Ms. Grace, this patient is critical."],[733,896,"We are prepping her for emergency surgery."],[966,1106,"Surgery? Did she pay?"],[1156,1309,"Doctor's duty is to save lives first."],[1446,1580,"Bullshit \"saves lives\"!"],[1636,1960,"My family owns this hospital now, you follow my rules."],[2046,2113,"No payment?"],[2376,2460,"Then let her rot."],[2569,2723,"Just another dead beggar."],[2780,2893,"The fee is too expensive."],[2893,2993,"Let me operate her first."],[2993,3076,"She will pay later."],[3119,3346,"Look, no money, you dig her grave!"],[3346,3493,"Get her out of my sight, now!"],[3536,3639,"Ms. Grace, please!"],[4070,4226,"How dare you hit me!"],[4263,4413,"Yeah, well you better hope she makes it,"],[4413,4563,"or you're gonna regret breathing!"],[4603,4746,"Doctor, she's crashing, no pulse."],[5096,5179,"I'll meet my mom..."],[5289,5446,"And dad... finally..."],[5863,5986,"No more pain in..."],[6383,6413,"Lina."]],"43":[[86,133,"I'm sorry."],[296,373,"She's gone."],[786,930,"Lina, my mom was back."],[1003,1106,"We were gonna be happy."],[1133,1213,"Shut up!"],[1316,1463,"Dead trash belongs in the gutter."],[1463,1593,"Get it out of here now!"],[1936,2193,"Grace, you are an absolute monster!"],[2206,2423,"James, destroy this place now!"],[2456,2506,"Try it!"],[2619,2723,"I own these walls."],[2839,3008,"You can't, hundreds of patients'"],[3028,3216,"lives rely on this hospital."],[3216,3447,"Fine, but if one patient struggles,"],[3447,3633,"I will evacuate this whole place"],[3633,3846,"and every cesspool will be blown up!"],[4096,4216,"Threaten me all you want!"],[4320,4560,"Cross me and you'll wish you were dead."],[4903,5200,"James, I want you to look up every crime"],[5200,5350,"that Jacob's committed as Senator."],[5410,5500,"Follow the funds."],[5553,5833,"Any bribes, stolen funds, everything."],[5950,6143,"I want these parasites eradicated."],[6200,6260,"Understood."]],"44":[[566,656,"Disgusting."],[753,1030,"That lunatic crippled my son,"],[1045,1226,"robbed him of fatherhood."],[1226,1446,"The Harris bloodline ends with him."],[1446,1623,"She even stole our house."],[1719,1986,"I want her skinned alive."],[2043,2306,"That old hag slapped me at the hospital today."],[2363,2473,"She declared war."],[2539,2656,"We need to end her now."],[2700,2916,"Uncle Robert, you have the military token."],[2916,3036,"Send troops. Crush her!"],[3200,3553,"She and that mercenary of hers are too sneaky."],[3583,3703,"We're powerless against them."],[4106,4266,"Wait, if they're that powerful,"],[4266,4439,"could she really be the Minister of Defense?"],[4496,4746,"Bullshit, I dug deep, she's just a retired grunt."],[4800,5010,"What? That scheming bitch!"],[5010,5106,"She even lied to her own daughter."],[5120,5433,"Doesn't matter who she is, she fights like a war god."],[5493,5833,"So the question is, how do we kill a war god?"],[5910,5973,"Call them."],[5986,6134,"Call Jacob. If they send an army,"],[6150,6326,"no flesh survives artillery."],[6326,6596,"Jacob's negotiating with Rubia Nation's leaders."],[6670,6793,"Everyone has weaknesses."],[6853,7063,"And that little brat Mia..."],[7159,7256,"is hers."]],"45":[[70,136,"Her weakness."],[220,329,"That little brat Mia."],[400,656,"Snatch the girl and the old hag will kneel."],[673,729,"Perfect."],[759,1153,"I'll torture Mia to death in front of her bitch mother."],[1206,1566,"Make her regret ever crossing us."],[1939,2113,"Mom, is this really our house?"],[2456,2593,"Always, ok?"],[2626,2803,"And look, I promised you no more suffering."],[2873,3008,"You're gonna have a good life"],[3021,3194,"from here on out, okay?"],[3250,3363,"You're the best mom ever."],[3570,3756,"I'm so sorry that you had to suffer."],[3896,3946,"I love you."],[4560,4633,"Mia?"],[4816,4893,"Hey, where's..."],[4970,5029,"Madam."],[5113,5160,"Where's Mia?"],[5243,5450,"Miss Mia went to go visit Lina's grave."],[5583,5626,"Alone?"],[5739,5846,"Why would she go alone?"],[5976,6156,"Can't bear to let that girl out of her sight."],[7650,8059,"We finally had hope, and now you're gone."],[8216,8283,"Don't worry."],[8416,8576,"Mom and I are going to save everyone."],[8670,8843,"We won't let anyone suffer like us."],[9363,9523,"Oh, you won't live to see that day."]],"46":[[946,1046,"Why are you doing this?"],[1090,1206,"Why am I doing this?"],[1286,1397,"I'm doing this because of you"],[1398,1546,"and that bitch of your mothers!"],[1546,1630,"It's time for revenge!"],[1723,1883,"No, you did this to yourself!"],[1883,1919,"Shut up!"],[2056,2226,"You and your mother did this to me,"],[2226,2356,"and you're gonna pay with your lives!"],[2476,2636,"My mom is the Minister of Defense."],[2666,2903,"If you touch me, she will destroy you!"],[2906,3023,"The Minister of Defense."],[3093,3260,"Your mom is a pathetic old grunt."],[3333,3483,"Grace dug up the truth about your mother."],[3553,3674,"Your mother sold herself out"],[3688,3896,"to high-ranking officers for money!"],[3896,4036,"She'd do anything for a paycheck!"],[4066,4120,"You liar!"],[4173,4333,"Don't talk about my mom like that!"],[4333,4406,"She is a hero!"],[4450,4560,"Stop wasting time."],[4603,4710,"Grab that little bitch!"],[4750,4770,"Now!"],[4846,4983,"No, no, let me go!"],[5026,5103,"Bad luck, Mia."],[5153,5326,"These two will have a little fun with you."],[5383,5529,"Let's see how your mom,"],[5573,5786,"your hero mom, will help you now."],[5939,6176,"What your hero mom can do about this, huh?"]],"47":[[36,206,"Anyone hurt my daughter?"],[266,600,"If anyone hurts her, you will die."],[840,896,"Pathetic."],[1676,1743,"Mom, you're here."],[1916,2071,"You crippled my son."],[2086,2276,"How dare you show your face?"],[2276,2400,"He reaped what he sowed."],[2630,2800,"Get in here! Kill her! Kill her now!"],[3986,4039,"Lunatic!"],[4089,4253,"How are you doing this? We are family!"],[4370,4686,"This is to avenge everyone that you destroyed."],[4736,4776,"David!"],[5386,5529,"Leave him alone."]],"48":[[356,603,"You are out of control!"],[856,1036,"David! My son!"],[1426,1580,"You're a fucking monster!"],[1710,1900,"You've killed my son!"],[1956,2130,"I'm gonna destroy you!"],[2663,2856,"Yeah, well they deserved a whole lot more."],[2936,2996,"And guess what?"],[3110,3189,"You're next."],[3239,3339,"Men, take aim."],[3546,3773,"You're not so fucking tough now, are you?"],[3889,4063,"Why don't you beg me and I'll make sure that they"],[4079,4273,"make headshots so you die quick."],[4306,4706,"Don't worry. Today, justice is gonna be served."],[4833,4900,"Justice?"],[5050,5283,"Have you looked around to see who's here with you?"],[5370,5473,"It's just us."],[5576,5623,"Aim!"],[5823,5916,"Hold your fire!"]],"49":[[20,113,"Hold your fire!"],[203,356,"Do you remember why you wear the uniform?"],[433,546,"To protect your country."],[609,690,"To defend the weak."],[766,886,"Not to serve a monster."],[1033,1126,"Look at what you've become."],[1276,1476,"How many atrocities has Robert committed?"],[1586,1677,"And now you point guns"],[1691,1923,"at the very people you swore to protect."],[1923,2016,"Alright, stand down."],[2236,2403,"I am Senator Jacob's father."],[2510,2769,"And if anybody else harms our family..."],[2873,3119,"Your family will die like he did."],[3146,3250,"We have families to protect."],[3286,3316,"Ready!"],[3413,3460,"Cowards!"],[3523,3736,"By the authority of the Minister of Defense,"],[3789,3926,"hold your fire!"],[3996,4160,"That's the minister's personal insignia,"],[4189,4300,"it's impossible to forge."],[4329,4426,"The design is classified."],[4489,4593,"Drop your guns now."]],"50":[[13,173,"So you're the minister."],[210,313,"Jacob's mother."],[386,636,"The woman who adopted Jacob."],[733,793,"David?"],[903,946,"David?"],[1043,1109,"David!"],[1109,1193,"David, wake up!"],[1193,1286,"Please, wake up!"],[1469,1550,"You killed him."],[1723,1846,"I'll gut you myself!"],[1930,2206,"She's got the Minister's insignia."],[2206,2266,"Lies!"],[2319,2619,"She forged it. Call Jacob! Expose this fraud."],[2693,2766,"Yes!"],[2910,3013,"I'll call Jacob."],[3100,3443,"And he will expose your lying ass."],[3676,3746,"Jacob?"],[3860,3976,"It's your father."],[3993,4106,"Dad? What's wrong?"],[4136,4596,"Your mother killed Sophia and David."],[4750,4916,"Now she's threatening to kill us."],[5006,5220,"I need you to get here right now."],[5276,5379,"I'll be there in 10 minutes."],[5483,5629,"Run while you still can."],[5729,6039,"Once Jacob gets here, you'll be begging for mercy."],[6156,6443,"I've been waiting for years,"],[6673,6783,"to settle this debt."],[7066,7186,"What's ten more minutes?"],[7240,7370,"Jacob and Robert's files."],[7443,7536,"Every dirty secret."],[7779,8059,"Time to take down this little game they're playing."]],"51":[[323,450,"Oh, here you are."],[516,596,"There's my boy."],[720,759,"Son."],[893,1035,"That's her. That's the woman"],[1049,1166,"who killed David and Sophia."],[1166,1300,"She threatened to slaughter us all."],[1346,1433,"Don't worry, Grace."],[1506,1683,"Justice will be served."],[1766,2063,"I want you to kneel and confess"],[2300,2656,"and explain the stolen funds now."],[2856,2939,"You're delusional."],[3036,3113,"Aim your weapons."],[3376,3503,"Here we go again."],[3623,3913,"By direct order of President Lewis Scott,"],[4000,4176,"I am the new minister."],[4246,4420,"And you, Zoe Miller,"],[4483,4736,"are just a murderous traitor to be jailed."],[4806,4953,"You know that's impossible, right?"],[5023,5203,"It's funny, but impossible."],[5253,5350,"Beg on your knees"],[5423,5596,"and bark like the dog you are."],[5666,6096,"Maybe I'll make prison for you less painful."],[6173,6370,"You gutless snake! She saved your life!"],[6426,6593,"By the President's direct order,"],[6646,6823,"interfere and you die where you stand."],[7006,7043,"It's okay."],[7156,7293,"Just comply."],[7383,7456,"Mom, don't go."],[7527,7609,"Please."],[8256,8320,"Mom!"]],"52":[[90,236,"The President arrives."],[526,726,"It's an honor to have you here, Mr. President."],[793,833,"A toast."],[966,1006,"To you."],[1076,1163,"To you, Jacob."],[1300,1413,"And all that served the nation."],[2560,2719,"Shall we begin the ceremony?"],[3033,3066,"Yes."],[3173,3346,"It's your big day becoming the Minister of..."],[3410,3523,"Not Minister of Defense."],[3673,3746,"As the President."],[4203,4236,"Treason."],[4266,4346,"I don't want rebellion."],[4420,4510,"I want what's mine."],[4573,4766,"The Presidency suits me better."],[4863,5183,"Everything you have, I gave it to you."],[5256,5370,"And I could take it all away."],[5670,5856,"Sign the resignation. Now."],[6389,6473,"Never!"],[7906,8046,"Jacob becomes President."],[8073,8376,"Oh, and Ruby Nation's leaders have pledged their"],[8413,8600,"full support and backing for me."],[8653,8763,"You're selling the country?"],[8800,8896,"Congratulations, Uncle."],[9006,9096,"The throne is ours."],[9166,9379,"I surrendered Jacob on the battlefield to"],[9413,9586,"keep from compromising my cover."],[9736,9913,"But you should thank Zoe for raising you."],[9913,10233,"It's because of her kindness that you became Senator."],[10306,10483,"You wouldn't have been a good man if I raised you."],[10543,10759,"You told me Zoe took me hostage on the battlefield."],[10783,10926,"What was I supposed to do?"],[10966,11203,"Compromise my big plan by telling you the truth?"],[11353,11563,"All these years, I was your pawn?"],[11593,11673,"So now you know."],[12326,12476,"Oh, Robert."],[12656,12773,"You arrogant fool."]],"53":[[33,143,"Why are you laughing?"],[189,263,"You're a dead man."],[616,659,"Sign it!"],[770,876,"In your dreams."],[956,1063,"You wanna play this the hard way?"],[1116,1169,"Pin him down!"],[1343,1530,"You are gonna sign this."],[1936,2219,"Touch him, and I will skin you alive."],[2303,2339,"No."],[2419,2510,"She was locked up."],[2573,2623,"How did..."],[2630,2757,"Minister Zoe's imprisonment"],[2774,2919,"was strategic theater."],[2919,3106,"To lure these traitors into the open."],[3160,3260,"Every move"],[3315,3539,"served to expose Robert's conspiracy."],[3539,3679,"As warriors of Valoria,"],[3679,3883,"we serve Minister of Defence, Zoe Miller,"],[3933,4083,"and President Louis Scott."],[4163,4203,"Always."],[4466,4543,"Bravo!"],[4693,4783,"Very brave words."],[4923,5033,"Coming from a corpse."],[5300,5363,"Showtime!"],[5473,5689,"Meet Rubia Nation's finest killers."],[5836,6010,"Let the slaughter begin."],[6050,6086,"You wanna?"],[6136,6286,"Try to get past me first."]],"54":[[523,586,"Zoe!"],[1180,1516,"Don't worry. My men have this place surrounded."],[1576,1719,"You'll all get to die together."],[1766,2016,"James, show him."],[2943,3236,"At the cemetery was when I realized,"],[3313,3536,"Jacob was being manipulated by Robert."],[3573,3933,"Under Robert's provocation, he grew hostile"],[3983,4386,"towards me and towards the Republic of Valoria."],[4479,4746,"That is why President Lewis and I"],[4820,5206,"arranged this little act so that we could gather up"],[5226,5523,"to seek all of those who wanted to harm Valoria."],[5656,5776,"So that's the truth."],[5776,6193,"My own father used me all along."],[6296,6383,"Arrest them."],[6873,6963,"No way."]],"55":[[0,233,"Life imprisonment to the deepest dungeons."],[296,329,"Take them!"],[353,493,"No, I won't lose to you!"],[506,656,"I won't lose to you like this!"],[683,713,"No!"],[1406,1523,"You suffered too much."],[1523,1625,"When this ends,"],[1630,1836,"I'll give you that grand wedding you deserve."],[1836,2216,"For this nation, I would do it all over again."],[2276,2576,"Hey, Mom, you and the President?"],[2783,2826,"Mia."],[3043,3116,"Meet your father."],[3670,3876,"Back then, we had to protect"],[3890,4120,"the borders of Valoria."],[4120,4210,"We had no choice."],[4296,4456,"We had to hide your true identity."],[4576,4756,"But now that everything is resolved,"],[4850,5003,"we can finally tell you the truth."],[5146,5656,"President Louis, he's your biological father."],[5693,5826,"Mia, I'm sorry."],[6029,6360,"At the time, my position as president wasn't secure yet."],[6466,6676,"I had to conceal you and your mother's identities"],[6676,6776,"to protect you both."],[6866,7056,"I've let you suffer far too long."],[7129,7270,"Please, give me a chance"],[7270,7393,"to make it up to you and your mother."],[8066,8209,"How can I resent heroes?"],[8329,8525,"My mother defends the borders,"],[8550,8850,"you lead the nation."],[8850,8903,"I'm proud."],[9616,10043,"From this day, Mia Scott will be Valoria's princess."],[10109,10236,"And we can finally be together."],[10363,10409,"Always."]]}